dmca.title: REMOVED per counter-notification and withdrawal of notice to Google
dmca.body:
Dear Sirs,

We are providing notification of a copyright infringement pursuant to the Digital Millennium Copyright Act.

The domain name refinance.net previously pointed to the server of Pipeline Media, Inc. (69.63.139.101). Pursuant to a domain name lease agreement, Pipeline Media operated the website refinance.net and developed content (see screenshots 1A-1F, 2, and 3).

[private]/IdentityWeb, Inc. redirected the domain refinance.net to new servers (DNS1.COUNSELWEB.COM   66.102.140.196 and DNS2.COUNSELWEB.COM   206.117.59.250) and uploaded content which is a replica of the content developed and owned by Pipeline Media, Inc. (see screenshots 1A-1F, 2, and 3).

Please immediately remove from your index the entire website which is infringing on the copyrighted content developed and owned by Pipeline Media.

The most frequent search queries used to located www.refinance.net are:
Refinance
Refinance mortgage
Refinance home
Refinance home loan
Refinance loan
Mortgage calculator(s)
Refinance debt
Debt consolidation
How to refinance
Refinancing home loans
Consolidating debt

I have a good faith belief that use of the material in this manner complained of is not authorized by Pipeline Media, Inc., the copyright owner of the relevant content, or the law.

I declare under penalty of perjury that the information in this notification is accurate and that I am authorized to act on behalf of Pipeline Media, Inc., the exclusive owner of the copyright that is infringed.

Do not hesitate to contact me with any information
